    <description>&gt;**The Hag**
Neutral killing
**Passive: Unholy vitality**
If you are attacked at night while you have a hex active, you will activate the hex and draw the life energy from the victims to survive the attack. 
**Day ability: Hex**
_(day, infinite uses, 2 day cool down)_ Hex three players. If none of them are dead in two days time, the hex will activate and kill them all. They will be informed of being hexed, but not of who else is hexed.
**Night ability: Mind warp**
_(infinite uses, 1-day cool down)_ Cause a player to receive incorrect feedback from their abilities tonight. 
**Night ability: Mind numb**
_(infinite uses, 1-day cool down)_ Occupy everyone who you have hexed.

Standards NK goal</description>
    
